{
  "voice_id": "7kXNOCqiaLdszL0OEXks",
  "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
  "voice_settings": {
    "stability": 0.65,
    "similarity_boost": 0.65,
    "style": 0.0,
    "speed": 1.1,
    "use_speaker_boost": true
  },
  "pronunciation_dictionary_locators": [
    {
      "pronunciation_dictionary_id": "AhK3J8mZDRoShxfoJLk6",
      "version_id": "pFvyQBbxEBKyF7C3IHpy"
    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Five extension points. Two capabilities.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8bac0d3a5f8d56d4878d101d76022d0ea485ad13ee2eefa5a09e84b45146bb01",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 2.2755555555555556,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Three patterns. Anthropic just published their own playbook for running Claude Code in a large codebase.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e384ddff272bab9e268594e5309a440c9f0745a42080ae10a3c51d06803e5f24",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 6.594467120181406,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 5
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "And the part most teams miss is this. The harness matters more than the model.",
      "checksum": "sha256:65ed438ddf6f42714911183a047bea70d3bf7fa86e4dd1b8962495029be41112",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 4.504671201814059,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 21
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "This is Part 1 of a brand-new series. Claude Code at scale.",
      "checksum": "sha256:498aa231039e7c31a10e8292d531bf60f6b4f165d6786f608759b910341dccd1",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 3.8545124716553287,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 36
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "So here is what is in the playbook. And here is the order Anthropic says to build it in.",
      "checksum": "sha256:09fde3f9d5064921ca378b93b02b29a694a0b6c71fc74d1124befac972b99cb9",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 5.2477097505668935,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 48
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "The post is from Anthropic's Applied A I team.",
      "checksum": "sha256:277d3f87a6afc2261748892b602781fe01033c77cea6b37a37fd545a33eca568",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 67
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Krifcher, Lee, Concannon, and five others from Anthropic's Applied A I team.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c4ef92511f7d7911fa808eed382ac5e7956566cb5a8738dbf24863c534fb36a8",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 4.922630385487528,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 76
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Published today as a 5 minute read on the Claude blog.",
      "checksum": "sha256:dc2ecb2ba24772c797f63d9576a3c9f9de979e346e01fa77f021de1c46d2addc",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 88
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "The series is called Claude Code at scale.",
      "checksum": "sha256:15cba883de635b578b54ff0f735fa60c37d47390bbad12ea28b5051d87cd6b99",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 2.2755555555555556,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 99
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "This is Part 1. And the post lays out one thesis right at the top.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f76345d958db39506900ac344b81a3a70df489352624f7aba1308f40be93e327",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 4.783310657596372,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 107
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "The ecosystem around the model, what Anthropic calls the harness, decides how Claude Code performs more than the model alone.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2f5508d5c2fa91a872402185bcd101169dcaddc771e59ffacb178d2ba93ce376",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 8.266303854875284,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 122
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Everything that follows is a breakdown of that harness.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5e99dbf60f23b3f857b46c755491c58b9c940eb00a3671079e32c4e426334e10",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 142
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Anthropic says Claude Code is now running in production across multi-million-line monorepos, decades-old legacy systems, and at organizations with thousands of developers.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b55b659be9ce518161e628f0a33f2b8a73b50bfcccd656983242ea62da4c785f",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 10.588299319727891,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 151
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Even on languages teams don't usually associate with A I coding tools.",
      "checksum": "sha256:aab5a77c148159fe36797beca020f72a3af0a22f6e381bd0fd652d2cc5317cf7",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 4.551111111111111,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 173
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "C, C plus plus, C sharp, Java, P H P. Anthropic notes Claude Code performs better than most teams expect in those cases.",
      "checksum": "sha256:988fbe6798e53429520c4f787c2ff48fb5dd789aa5c51c0e828a95a3cacc9021",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 9.520181405895691,
      "word_count": 23,
      "words_offset": 185
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Especially as of recent model releases. So how does Claude Code actually navigate a codebase this big?",
      "checksum": "sha256:e3b73a809c6179fad9e14200077c09f9baa115a1194ba6e29dd74512831567f1",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 6.6873469387755105,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 208
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "The article explains it. Older A I coding tools relied on rag retrieval.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f3817cb1bac8a5e29434a63b3e81741b098f959f73e2a0fd16c2843f213671c9",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 4.6439909297052155,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 225
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Embed the whole repo. Retrieve chunks at query time.",
      "checksum": "sha256:af1d5ed408d892fc54f969fd1b8cbf8538d89ca72930361d7f48823449215b93",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 238
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "At large scale, that breaks. Embedding pipelines can't keep up with active engineering teams.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6e7001afa117bb76093825eae75757e3a970396e265df02acb310372720ff4c1",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 5.6656689342403626,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 247
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "By the time a developer queries the index, it might point at a function the team renamed two weeks ago.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9a86c6b6e218329a04f7fe075fd2decc65ff2685a99930d944bb03b4289aadaf",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 5.526349206349207,
      "word_count": 20,
      "words_offset": 261
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "Or reference a module deleted in the last sprint.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e96ed2e12b0f7f800c346eb9bd4d9698683e7608aabceb1578b1da7e427793fc",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 2.6006349206349206,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 281
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "With no indication that either is out of date.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a6cb2ad24fb6c11522c061628b4b413d6d096184e7d91109d40259a71bf734ae",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 2.507755102040816,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 290
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "Claude Code does it differently. Agentic search.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ee32b27d1c48212d4ee15938ea492461abd9200bc629c72a5486ebbb1725ae5e",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 299
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "No embedding pipeline. No central index.",
      "checksum": "sha256:783cce9c4d137f40b047f4ee8958feddc2d67094bf7589b4483d269fcc16ac46",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 2.36843537414966,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 306
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "Each developer's instance works from the current codebase, reading files the way an engineer would.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ede4f40a5f46ab6c3e5186036a069abde107c752b1dcdb973f04b3bcbd7c8e7c",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 5.479909297052155,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 312
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "This is the harness chart from Anthropic's article.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fdb810651182b24481a6d451e91927a5afc97ca444866afe89b5167c363fb0dd",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 2.693514739229025,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 327
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "Figure one. The playbook in a single table.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4114c2f10389451b49c9347e144602e5c1737c4a63d272e5568a67ae35508412",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 335
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "Five extension points. CLAUDE dot M D files.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cf4a1eb6039b782343ae0569ad40a2f7e882db657851fe32ea6dd77c7654aa61",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 343
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "Hooks. Skills. Plugins. And M C P servers.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ae643e39185cdfa3ec5c02f1d4376bb144f1e26b89e2dbaff37c1b3bd02dbd8b",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 351
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "Then two additional capabilities. L S P integrations and sub-agents.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9a9fe6073265263997b912434276b2a368a88fa3a7c81f1722a0306824893cd9",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 5.015510204081632,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 359
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "Seven components in total. And Anthropic is explicit about one thing.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1dd77ee3f305268cf1b2fdc6bac4d333d0ec6d59233b9010574e4e295b51421e",
      "wav": "chunk-30.wav",
      "duration": 4.365351473922902,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 369
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "text": "The order in which teams build them matters.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ceb81b4000a8747f75c96fb5dcef9e6e6d8eab1cb2910de0df748032ab0df76a",
      "wav": "chunk-31.wav",
      "duration": 2.182675736961451,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 380
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "text": "Each layer builds on the one before it. CLAUDE dot M D first.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4b76a3d700c31a8b0977ddce335f2d86fa0e10b0a158df91fb6e3ada168b89c9",
      "wav": "chunk-32.wav",
      "duration": 4.179591836734694,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 388
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "text": "M C P last. Building the layers out of order is the most common mistake teams make.",
      "checksum": "sha256:66feb0b2a205cd469f12a75639b8a9bfc922501ed0311ab20a43d3e82e16b588",
      "wav": "chunk-33.wav",
      "duration": 4.922630385487528,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 401
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "text": "Here is the breakdown card by card. Card one.",
      "checksum": "sha256:525ba0863bbce14cc35402239f078c42b644dd498e99578973b19b8a20450f2e",
      "wav": "chunk-34.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 418
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "text": "CLAUDE dot M D files come first. Context files Claude reads automatically at every session.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8efb40b58588074d847bfcdc98c4bc8cd5b43ef84996923a1e84009bc7e9e387",
      "wav": "chunk-35.wav",
      "duration": 7.523265306122449,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 427
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "text": "Card two. Hooks make the setup self-improving.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4d3b7b6b41fea95d139897d581d72b13f48dc9c6a7f9487fc7218ca8fdfae6e2",
      "wav": "chunk-36.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 442
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "text": "A stop hook can reflect on a session and propose CLAUDE dot M D updates while context is fresh.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d8b52b2c9a52f077fe318196996de77cf1b830727b07abdb19f60b47be57edff",
      "wav": "chunk-37.wav",
      "duration": 6.0836281179138325,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 449
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "text": "Card three. Skills keep expertise on-demand through progressive disclosure.",
      "checksum": "sha256:515d253041180a309d00056ad71daa1b63f8d1e7887b4d4141bc69724ff3aa26",
      "wav": "chunk-38.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 468
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "text": "A security review skill loads when Claude assesses code for vulnerabilities.",
      "checksum": "sha256:dc0171cf9daf3b0de1fd405ba75187d17bd1b1420b556b7d349af6db05ce8fce",
      "wav": "chunk-39.wav",
      "duration": 4.4117913832199545,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 477
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "text": "Card four. Plugins distribute what works.",
      "checksum": "sha256:693d2b6d803ebcbabdb09245e9ab956c0ba0943d9822826ab1013f946208fd75",
      "wav": "chunk-40.wav",
      "duration": 2.507755102040816,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 488
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "text": "They bundle skills, hooks, and M C P configurations into one installable package.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2f8f386f868b84a2e3d6c95f11559f4e69e74fe0cc7575441c1d6908ec969f0f",
      "wav": "chunk-41.wav",
      "duration": 5.2477097505668935,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 494
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "text": "Anthropic gives a concrete example. A large retail organization built a skill connecting Claude to their internal analytics platform, then distributed it as a plugin before the broad rollout.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e9e6d7778e22a96843726d2e5626b7760f1d41ec2afb92ae55c34c389d4b5005",
      "wav": "chunk-42.wav",
      "duration": 11.517097505668934,
      "word_count": 30,
      "words_offset": 507
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "text": "Card five. L S P integrations. Symbol-level precision.",
      "checksum": "sha256:25b86ae91c2b594b3290fd0f325dd1c4e6eabdf8ff6dd85613da9074b474111d",
      "wav": "chunk-43.wav",
      "duration": 3.622312925170068,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 537
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "text": "One enterprise software company deployed L S P org-wide before their Claude Code rollout.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9dc56ddee3cc36209b09d8fe4ab8a0539319802b41048525e3d1c423f99a253f",
      "wav": "chunk-44.wav",
      "duration": 5.201269841269841,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 545
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "text": "Specifically to make C and C plus plus navigation reliable at scale.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c771eb64e86a285f6ccde77b70c2b9b33975a1abcd17879b0648cfd242938127",
      "wav": "chunk-45.wav",
      "duration": 4.08671201814059,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 559
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "text": "Card six. M C P servers extend everything.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8aa2ae6e33b0033578ee9c9f8d47782cf19b0d4760509a674218f03843d702f2",
      "wav": "chunk-46.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 571
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "text": "The most sophisticated teams expose structured search as a tool Claude can call directly.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2d4128eab3e186db7678076634982472a99d749b5d1a1cbb098a0f496f3a7e64",
      "wav": "chunk-47.wav",
      "duration": 5.294149659863946,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 579
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "text": "And the article calls out the common confusion here.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f5a1921eb4a022ef9438bace6a583af191d04f9383163725f169d24ecdfc3106",
      "wav": "chunk-48.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 593
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "text": "Teams build M C P first. Don't. It comes last.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4d528ab95e6d3fcaad602a7dffe9c3e77e289dbf0fefdde4be54fec861935102",
      "wav": "chunk-49.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 602
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "text": "Card seven. Sub-agents. Isolated Claude instances that take a task, do the work, and return only the final result to the parent.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b36e2284d2f3e378d40ac43f155c746ed4db8ba9b377fe6762912d7fa4fffee0",
      "wav": "chunk-50.wav",
      "duration": 8.126984126984127,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 612
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "text": "Quick beat. If this playbook is useful to you, hit subscribe.",
      "checksum": "sha256:594364a8b8f6fa41391973fe38b025c84abfd6f4314361a1bfec373d945ed7e1",
      "wav": "chunk-51.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 634
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "text": "Part 2 of the series drops next. Pattern one.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a091e109e96229ebdc66622880b966f856d5600cf177740799e55aaf06750875",
      "wav": "chunk-52.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 645
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "text": "Make the codebase navigable at scale. Anthropic lays out six sub-patterns.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e246871aa00c6fc198b31286398215eafd039fff00e2803c7a878b390f698a1c",
      "wav": "chunk-53.wav",
      "duration": 4.783310657596372,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 654
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "text": "One. Keep CLAUDE dot M D files lean and layered. Root file for the big picture, subdirectory files for local conventions.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b144062e34e5835970332a32bbb4935dd9d3033247b508662620f1653ab56e87",
      "wav": "chunk-54.wav",
      "duration": 8.034104308390022,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 665
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "text": "Everything else drifts into noise. Two. Initialize in subdirectories, not at the repo root.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0b14e8902d69039793762ad81c9e410511ba512d00076d14aa2afa2486a49804",
      "wav": "chunk-55.wav",
      "duration": 6.315827664399093,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 686
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "text": "Claude automatically walks up the directory tree and loads every CLAUDE dot M D it finds along the way.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e646095c97891470d1d36d01a6eeba7e16c3ba2fd96c91176b2a6d659fa9114e",
      "wav": "chunk-56.wav",
      "duration": 6.640907029478458,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 700
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "text": "Three. Scope test and lint commands per subdirectory.",
      "checksum": "sha256:79333b7bc7ede1fbb0a67f044b2df53fcfccd43f84d5765047e6cc11e667f39c",
      "wav": "chunk-57.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 719
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "text": "Running the full suite when Claude changed one service wastes context on irrelevant output.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7004474e961976f9a2e0f39e570014ea8a275e696c17e522f75a692ff5db889e",
      "wav": "chunk-58.wav",
      "duration": 5.38702947845805,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 727
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "text": "Four. Use dot-gitignore plus permissions-dot-deny in dot-claude slash settings-dot-json.",
      "checksum": "sha256:dc7047816a72d848ea12a7c7e4b73cff196e2f6f878d13582ed85ecf7a4cccaa",
      "wav": "chunk-59.wav",
      "duration": 5.897868480725624,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 741
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "text": "Version-controlled exclusions, so every developer gets the same noise reduction.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1f8835476a26c51bef1c61700d8ed0f1e065549668fd8413fe79bf34091bd575",
      "wav": "chunk-60.wav",
      "duration": 4.783310657596372,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 750
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "text": "Five. Build codebase maps when the directory structure doesn't do the work.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fc5e31edb067fb578156133e967fbb1a10247c357c7af325df1ea8d19ab10618",
      "wav": "chunk-61.wav",
      "duration": 4.783310657596372,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 760
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "text": "A lightweight markdown file at the repo root listing each top-level folder with a one-line description.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ea5ae9769ac7cd26c5f0f6183098d728850a2b07eda2d60b21cc4ad977888e1c",
      "wav": "chunk-62.wav",
      "duration": 5.897868480725624,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 772
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "text": "Six. Run L S P so Claude searches by symbol, not by string.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b9071ea2a9fa7007cad9f4ac311f63310a9a0866c00bd5514898c55542861ca4",
      "wav": "chunk-63.wav",
      "duration": 4.272471655328798,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 788
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "text": "Grep for a common function name in a large codebase returns thousands of matches.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3014469996b804dc46741efead84b669d2be6a924d8f33c929da0721974267be",
      "wav": "chunk-64.wav",
      "duration": 4.4117913832199545,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 801
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "text": "L S P returns only the references that point to the same symbol.",
      "checksum": "sha256:505722ce2b546e5c509929db489e33ba51a56ba96cafa40866c7274bca6f20f6",
      "wav": "chunk-65.wav",
      "duration": 4.31891156462585,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 815
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "text": "Pattern two. Actively maintain CLAUDE dot M D files as models evolve.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ac344dad174dffef5d168b91e07ed32585a12f19877ac3cbedda5d382e87626e",
      "wav": "chunk-66.wav",
      "duration": 4.96907029478458,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 828
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "text": "Anthropic says instructions written for your current model can work against a future one.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4497695b79639cd813a0ac18fcde3cd3c3505b5ae8599093137204e4a84b44e7",
      "wav": "chunk-67.wav",
      "duration": 5.154829931972789,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 840
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "text": "Teams should expect a meaningful configuration review every three to six months.",
      "checksum": "sha256:63302a0f158f668bd293ab35c23ac1a5562a640ef18a007cb80fa854bd673064",
      "wav": "chunk-68.wav",
      "duration": 4.597551020408163,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 854
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "text": "Or whenever performance feels like it's plateaued after a major model release.",
      "checksum": "sha256:93ddc3951766be8c33c509592bffd6cbd8b6440db807ef0d10cc810bfa215275",
      "wav": "chunk-69.wav",
      "duration": 4.179591836734694,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 866
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "text": "The article gives one concrete example. A hook that intercepted file writes to enforce P four edit in a Perforce codebase.",
      "checksum": "sha256:93887bea8a88f1f09de0545bf2656a717277efae5d214b8d9481726934a1cb53",
      "wav": "chunk-70.wav",
      "duration": 7.012426303854875,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 878
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "text": "It became redundant the moment Claude Code added native Perforce mode.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d71b7d247117d0dce3067017cadeeefe87df14b012094cf0fb770b064bfdcd6d",
      "wav": "chunk-71.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 899
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "text": "This is the rollout-phases diagram from Anthropic's article.",
      "checksum": "sha256:52e76905d2af3a46c24ec0c3ad4bbe5db9de4866731b08f6ef5ec39870ecf125",
      "wav": "chunk-72.wav",
      "duration": 3.3436734693877552,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 910
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "text": "Figure two. Pattern three. Assign ownership.",
      "checksum": "sha256:52174781ee191e5a205a22036f9b018c1d62c05e8c463ab417ae6df8e446f0a5",
      "wav": "chunk-73.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 918
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "text": "Technical configuration alone doesn't drive adoption.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0513da8cd9e996cbf0a769fd867620ef55d41680c7030f6c7d9785ef882cbc67",
      "wav": "chunk-74.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 924
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "text": "The rollouts that spread fastest had a dedicated infrastructure investment before broad access.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1389aed967b9d3bc8e610d9c2e6620091e257bd469d9134bfa9edec437ea4d26",
      "wav": "chunk-75.wav",
      "duration": 5.61922902494331,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 930
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "text": "Anthropic names two concrete examples. At one company, a couple of engineers built a suite of plugins and M C Ps that were available on day one.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7666f3d0c1b0d4d52ab7ef54b7cdea7ffa1fdc2b98ec383efd8db53394649496",
      "wav": "chunk-76.wav",
      "duration": 8.498503401360544,
      "word_count": 27,
      "words_offset": 943
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "text": "At another, an entire team focused on managing A I coding tools had the infrastructure in place before the rollout began.",
      "checksum": "sha256:dfd587277ed9a986c4a800073c7a9824f235347c27aec8d735626b24f1fabeff",
      "wav": "chunk-77.wav",
      "duration": 7.198185941043084,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 970
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "text": "Anthropic calls the emerging role the agent manager.",
      "checksum": "sha256:35bda1dac2ce60916d6073347925375a7a7f19ce3ad58dc2aff311fa62515ba4",
      "wav": "chunk-78.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 991
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "text": "A hybrid P M slash engineer dedicated to managing the Claude Code ecosystem.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b8fde7a541c8bf843313dab37c6d85a7c03f54fa56a391f5a8ffb89535e6f06e",
      "wav": "chunk-79.wav",
      "duration": 4.876190476190477,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 999
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "text": "The minimum viable version is a D R I. One person with authority over settings, permissions, and CLAUDE dot M D conventions.",
      "checksum": "sha256:55f42254ba3310e092cad0327c616cd3006d94c49d82f04ff7c6a7a9347a30ee",
      "wav": "chunk-80.wav",
      "duration": 8.17342403628118,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 1012
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "text": "And the smoothest deployments establish a cross-functional working group early.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d984bb12e1a9b8d350fbbdb28c9af1117f87099584da50a6cd2196f8411b434e",
      "wav": "chunk-81.wav",
      "duration": 4.133151927437642,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 1034
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "text": "Engineering, information security, and governance representatives.",
      "checksum": "sha256:74f0f95b6ad7f109d5e1a8e26776eb5d024e9fcce5e8a2459c7b682ccf3f32c0",
      "wav": "chunk-82.wav",
      "duration": 4.040272108843538,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 1044
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "text": "Defining requirements together and building the rollout roadmap.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6faaf7b9e658598402bf612e129d2b3f086aade4e56fc4ac70275c23861beff7",
      "wav": "chunk-83.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 1050
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "text": "This is the getting-started checklist from Anthropic's article.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1bb3bf066313004bf4fad4954ce72dab23933bb84bded4fce0d0cc3f64cbc6c7",
      "wav": "chunk-84.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 1058
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "text": "Figure three. The action items at the end of the post.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d17194fe5aae9de98e98f8f150a0cae106f4d9b92f53e87cc235fce81019fcf0",
      "wav": "chunk-85.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 1066
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "text": "CLAUDE dot M D first. Then hooks, skills, plugins.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e54c55481904c5d449f340c1a8e4368bdafcc7fab0b126d66bbd78441c753de7",
      "wav": "chunk-86.wav",
      "duration": 3.7151927437641725,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 1077
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "text": "Then L S P and M C P. In that order. And one caveat from Anthropic.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ce615b1dea58bcf345efa84b0280dd039c22551cad67f07dc1f5608fcd496b73",
      "wav": "chunk-87.wav",
      "duration": 4.922630385487528,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 1086
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "text": "There are edge cases this article does not cover.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e7ad234fdd10213133aa3b5c920877c9baf8f6cdb5fc1d534c484acd5e132df4",
      "wav": "chunk-88.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 1102
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "text": "Codebases with hundreds of thousands of folders.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f4acd6c4b392cc93eece66a425f144f3b2b783619d077cf71f566f3af2ff549e",
      "wav": "chunk-89.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 1111
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "text": "Millions of files. Or legacy systems on non-Git version control.",
      "checksum": "sha256:827cb052df3e49852d6686b67e6528496fd12e5842e51c50770dcb63d0baae42",
      "wav": "chunk-90.wav",
      "duration": 4.08671201814059,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 1118
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "text": "The article says those will be addressed in future installments of the series.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f0dab9284bffd38dc3628516fc3bc00ce3c356051c4d0827408fd5e54c56471d",
      "wav": "chunk-91.wav",
      "duration": 3.947392290249433,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 1128
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "text": "So if your environment is in that bucket, Part 2 is the one to watch for.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3db2e9ebf7a41ab08b1e203c70b82f07d967982b74e3b56b669e864a901db10b",
      "wav": "chunk-92.wav",
      "duration": 4.08671201814059,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 1141
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "text": "The rest of us can start applying the playbook today.",
      "checksum": "sha256:748b6ea1cec9101e76272d55fc7bc377eae984cac13841305bf035e6dd3efc1a",
      "wav": "chunk-93.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 1157
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "text": "So that is Anthropic's playbook. The harness, the three patterns, and the order to build them in.",
      "checksum": "sha256:81e7d345465bc8cc328bc6f3a160273da7911718978fe32b5cfd20a669a0e9bd",
      "wav": "chunk-94.wav",
      "duration": 5.758548752834467,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 1167
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "text": "If you want to see how to actually build a harness like this, check out the Archon video.",
      "checksum": "sha256:830377468507d6166697d2cca5b9df5bfeb113c90f1480300eedf37c85b1f288",
      "wav": "chunk-95.wav",
      "duration": 4.272471655328798,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 1184
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "text": "Claude Code's harness builder. Link on screen.",
      "checksum": "sha256:99918c4d8ede88335c77b8480b1456308edd9da6c77db256c727aa97da1c7c70",
      "wav": "chunk-96.wav",
      "duration": 2.6006349206349206,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 1202
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "text": "Anthropic says the harness matters more than the model.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c6403db934f9629b459d916a48b12a334b5981c65b5c0919a5dac6845ffce14d",
      "wav": "chunk-97.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 1209
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "text": "Do you buy it? Or is it still mostly Claude doing the work?",
      "checksum": "sha256:2a703ddc31a64fa1fd7a03679209f3d9615095f4afc2cd7c154741067bda870b",
      "wav": "chunk-98.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 1218
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "text": "Drop your pick below. Harness or model. Which one is doing the work?",
      "checksum": "sha256:2de3d40f02de90954b084ac2a0234c4fd6b492607f832e03e14bf4a18ea21ca7",
      "wav": "chunk-99.wav",
      "duration": 4.365351473922902,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 1231
    }
  ]
}